    "breadcrumb": "OOP \u003e Debugging \u0026 Logging",
    "description": "Video Materials\nObject in our object-oriented programs can really be thought of as two different parts - the state and behavior of the object. When debugging, we may need to consider both parts of the object to determine what is really going on behind the scenes. So, let’s look at some ways we can explore the state of our program.",
